{"tid":264808,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"被休班警制服後昏迷不治 家屬入稟向多方索償","createTime":"2017-05-31T06:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T08:40:23.000Z","uid":44783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81ddf9f5b55602056c1472ba3736b2f10975a066","tid":264808,"uid":44783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:42:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170531/large/1496210506_1d4e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170531%2Flarge%2F1496210506_1d4e.gif&h=81a6f31c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男子曾洛培(30歲)在2014年7月於荃灣乘搭小巴途中，突稱銀包被偷並指控是坐於其後的休班警長所為，繼而涉拳打警長，曾由多名乘客合力制服。而<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">警員到場調查期間曾突然昏迷</span></strong>，送院後證實不治。曾洛培家屬入稟高等法院，控告該休班警、消防處處長、警務處處長，以及多名救護員和警員等，指曾遭毆打、非法禁錮以及延誤救援而導致失救而死，向眾人索償。<br />\n<br />\n原告曾業廣（譯音），被告依次為馮少文、香港政府、張志輝、謝有寶、消防處處長、江永輝、甘耀文、警務處處長、周永樂、王彥玲、王偉鴻、李軍志、連潤中（皆譯音）。原告指首、第三及四被告作為救護員及救護車指揮中心控制員，第六及七被告作為警員，均沒為曾提供適時的救援措施；而第九被告警長至第十三被告則在案發時毆打及非法禁錮曾，原告並指警方在處理被捕人士時缺乏指引及適當訓練。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無啦啦突然昏迷仲死埋<br />\nLAN 線都唔駛用<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8987d3cdc58dd2d19fe4ee98e2a4409dcc65a04","tid":264808,"uid":14606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T07:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://mopicer.com/Service/Image.ashx?key=MjAxMzAy&amp;f=R6Gk2kmR.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmopicer.com%2FService%2FImage.ashx%3Fkey%3DMjAxMzAy%26f%3DR6Gk2kmR.JPG&h=14a2a85e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f6da45275775c1a1398875149cfbc665555d897","tid":264808,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T07:39:56.000Z","msg":"郁手既好似唔止係休班警喎<br />\n咁開地圖炮去告...告唔告得入架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f4160962f929cfffc1157aa42c74c9166450afb","tid":264808,"uid":44783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T07:43:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>郁手既好似唔止係休班警喎<br />\n咁開地圖炮去告...告唔告得入架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而第九被告警長至第十三被告則在案發時毆打及非法禁錮曾<br />\n<br />\n呢D case 通常都有幾部CCTV 同一時間故障"},{"pid":"743a3dcd078477834817ed2872abe61f2693042c","tid":264808,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T07:45:41.000Z","msg":"律師定家屬諗出黎?留明學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b20df5c873d43a2c901b6c09fa5a69e2df64f54e","tid":264808,"uid":44783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T08:40:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>律師定家屬諗出黎?留明學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n應該係律師掛<br />\n告多幾個收幾次堂費"}]}